{"tid":1418774,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"辛苦大家喇！但我想提返你哋一樣嘢！","createTime":"2019-08-05T20:22:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T17:38:43.000Z","uid":217103,"like":87,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1b85b8d65f3362b04a8cc6b0377e7bc5c9f18dbe","tid":1418774,"uid":217103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:22:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我哋同黑警唔同嘅地方，<br />\n就係<span style=\"color: red;\">我哋唔係與民為敵，而係<strong>為民為戰</strong>！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家對住普通市民都應該要客氣啲，比多少少耐性，唔好一嚟就屌</span><br />\n<br />\n我知大家呢兩個月都辛苦，會有負面情緒，<br />\n但唔好對住市民咁快起曬鋼，試下好聲好氣講完唔啱先算<br />\n而家唔係話要攞民意，唔係話輿唔輿論，<br />\n而係我哋愛香港先出嚟，對香港市民(正常啲嘅) <br />\n都應該態度好啲！<br />\n當然嗰啲冇得救嘅on9仔就緊係屌柒佢啦<br />\n<br />\n未醒嘅人其實都係呢個極權下嘅受害者，<br />\n我地犧牲嘅係自由，而佢地失去嘅係思考。"},{"pid":"fa44b0dfa5ffe4573c289e8adda5431db0ab4a66","tid":1418774,"uid":217103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:24:40.000Z","msg":"光復香港時代革命！"},{"pid":"2844b3fa2ee48a4f3cbad17eb8d14524f259655e","tid":1418774,"uid":217103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:25:43.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"f24814b3fc9b7d40ce0a991069ebfa7ff6eddb95","tid":1418774,"uid":217103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:26:07.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"ce3b587b1589150efa026dd75f8ab51e2387a267","tid":1418774,"uid":217103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:26:17.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"4f7f2d0d455dab6a082054ab0f4511dec082af83","tid":1418774,"uid":217103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:26:29.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"b3cf9a4b88a86a2b9d973c21e57787f2833b0509","tid":1418774,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:26:40.000Z","msg":"建議］ p牌正負評顯示<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1415247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1415247</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n-------------------